Write python program to design calculator with following features:
a) basic arithmetic
b) scientific calculation
c) conversion in binary, octal, hexadecimal, decimal
d) temperature conversion
e) length conversion



Answer:


print("Name:Navdeep Singh Roll Number:2110992590/d2")

a=int(input("Enter first value"))
b=int(input("Enter second value"))
p=a+b
m=a-b
mp=a*b
d=a/b
cal=input("Enter any arthemethic operation to perform(+=p,-=m,*=mp./=d)")
if cal==p:
    print("The addition of two number is",p)
elif cal==m:
    print("The Subtraction of two number is",m)
elif cal==mp:
    print("The Multiplication of two number is",mp)
elif cal==d:
    print("The Division of two number is",d)
else:
    print("Enter from the given choices")

